Install Instructions for Components


IMIS
  Microsoft Azure: Windows Server: 
  Setup Open IMIS 
      Windows Server 2012 R2, 4 CPUs, 8GB RAM, 300GB Hard drive
      SQLite is needed to create .db3 databases that are compatible with the IMIS phones
          http://openimis.readthedocs.io/en/latest/web_application_installation.html#prerequisites 
  Install IIS
  Install and Configure SQL Server
  Install IMIS
  Install Windows Services
  APIs

